HEADWORD: Illimitation
<hw>Il*lim`it*a"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>il-</ets> not + <ets>limitation</ets>: cf. F.
<ets>illimitation</ets>.]</ety> <def>State of being illimitable; lack
of, or freedom from, limitation.</def> <rj><au>Bp. Hall.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

